KING OF BABYLON CONTEST.

01:11.439 --> 01:13.174
- IT ALWAYS SEEMS LIKE
SUCH A BIG DEAL AT THE TIME,

01:13.207 --> 01:14.308
AND THEN, LIKE, A WEEK LATER,

01:14.342 --> 01:15.843
YOU CAN'T EVEN
REMEMBER WHO WON.

01:15.876 --> 01:16.844
- ANGEL ESCOBAR.

01:16.877 --> 01:19.313
5'10", 175,

01:19.347 --> 01:22.283
28" WAIST, 9" COCK,

01:22.316 --> 01:24.552
AND A BIRTHMARK IN THE SHAPE
OF PLACIDO DOMINGO

01:24.585 --> 01:26.220
IN HIS INNER RIGHT THIGH.

01:26.254 --> 01:28.289
- WOW, YOU WERE
PAYING ATTENTION.

01:28.322 --> 01:30.358
- SHOULD I BE JEALOUS?

01:30.391 --> 01:31.792
- NO.

01:37.331 --> 01:39.300
- THINK I'LL SKIP DESSERT.

01:39.333 --> 01:40.534
- MAN, WHO CARES ABOUT
A BUNCH OF STEROID GYM BUNNIES

01:40.568 --> 01:42.436
DANCING AROUND
IN THEIR JOCKS ANYWAY?

01:42.470 --> 01:43.604
- WELL, CONSIDERING YOU FUCKED

01:43.637 --> 01:44.838
ALL OF LAST YEAR'S CONTESTANTS:
YOU.

01:44.872 --> 01:47.608
[laughter]

01:47.641 --> 01:48.742
- GOD, WHO WOULD DO THAT?

01:48.776 --> 01:50.311
- WHO WOULDN'T FUCK BRIAN?

01:50.344 --> 01:51.545
- NO.

01:51.579 --> 01:53.214
I MEAN STRIP IN FRONT OF ALL
THOSE PEOPLE.

01:53.247 --> 01:54.882
- FOR 1,000 BUCKS
AND A TRIP TO THE BAHAMAS?

01:54.915 --> 01:56.217
A LOT OF GUYS.

01:56.250 --> 01:57.485
- ESPECIALLY
WHEN YOU'RE ON DRUGS.

01:57.518 --> 02:02.856
PLEASE, YOU'LL DO ANYTHING.

02:02.890 --> 02:05.359
OOPS, SORRY.

02:05.393 --> 02:07.361
- BLAKE ACKNOWLEDGES
HIS ADDICTION,

02:07.395 --> 02:08.929
AND HE'S WORKING ON IT.

02:08.962 --> 02:12.500
- I'VE BEEN GOING TO MEETINGS
AT THE GAY AND LESBIAN CENTER.

02:12.533 --> 02:15.603
- MY, MY, AREN'T WE
A BUSY LITTLE BEE?

02:15.636 --> 02:18.939
SO, UM, WE'LL ALL MEET
IN FRONT OF BABYLON, 10:00?

02:18.972 --> 02:21.242
- I DON'T KNOW, I DON'T THINK
DAVID'S GOING TO WANT TO GO

02:21.275 --> 02:22.943
'CAUSE IT'S KIND OF LATE.

02:22.976 --> 02:24.912
- DOES HE ALREADY HAVE
HIS TEETH IN A GLASS BY THEN?

02:24.945 --> 02:27.181
- I'LL HAVE YOU KNOW HE GETS UP
AT 6:00 EVERY MORNING

02:27.215 --> 02:29.417
AND RUNS FIVE MILES,
WHILE YOU'RE STILL IN BED.

02:29.450 --> 02:32.753
- I FEEL THAT'S WHERE
I GET MY BEST CARDIO WORKOUT.

02:32.786 --> 02:34.455
- I'M SURE HE WOULD GO
IF I WANTED HIM TO.

02:34.488 --> 02:35.756
- UH-HUH.
- IT'S TRUE!

02:35.789 --> 02:38.659
- ALL RIGHT,
THEN MAKE SURE HE'S THERE.

02:38.692 --> 02:39.660
- ALL RIGHT, I WILL.

02:39.693 --> 02:40.661
- OKAY.
- OKAY.

02:40.694 --> 02:41.662
- GREAT.
- FINE.

02:41.695 --> 02:43.397
- SO YOU COMING?

02:43.431 --> 02:46.900
WELL, BABYLON ISN'T EXACTLY
A DRUG-FREE ENVIRONMENT.

02:46.934 --> 02:48.669
- YOU KNOW,
BLAKE'S A BIG BOY.

02:48.702 --> 02:51.605
WHY DON'T YOU LET HIM DECIDE?

02:51.639 --> 02:54.442
- I'M FINE.

02:54.475 --> 02:56.544
REALLY.

02:56.577 --> 02:57.545
- WE'RE IN.

02:57.578 --> 02:59.280
- HOORAY!

02:59.313 --> 03:02.416
ONLY IT'S STARTING TO FEEL
PERILOUSLY LIKE A COUPLES NIGHT,

03:02.450 --> 03:04.418
SEEING AS I'M
THE ONLY SINGLE BOY LEFT.

03:04.452 --> 03:06.487
- EXCUSE ME, WHAT THE FUCK
DO YOU THINK I AM?

03:06.520 --> 03:08.289
- ARE WE GOING TO BABYLON?

03:08.322 --> 03:09.757
- [laughs]

03:09.790 --> 03:10.824
- WHAT?

03:15.529 --> 03:17.931
- THOSE JEANS ARE ALL WORN
AND TOO TIGHT.

03:17.965 --> 03:19.800
- WHAT?

03:19.833 --> 03:22.970
- [mumbles]

03:23.003 --> 03:27.375
I SAID THOSE JEANS
ARE ALL WORN AND TOO TIGHT.

03:27.408 --> 03:29.410
HOW COME I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
IN THEM BEFORE?

03:29.443 --> 03:31.712
- I ONLY WEAR THEM WHEN
I DON'T HAVE CLEAN CLOTHES.

03:31.745 --> 03:34.448
- WELL, YOU MUST STOP DOING
LAUNDRY IMMEDIATELY.

03:34.482 --> 03:35.783
- [chuckles]

03:35.816 --> 03:37.718
- HEY...

03:37.751 --> 03:38.986
DO YOU FEEL LIKE GOING OUT?

03:39.019 --> 03:41.355
TONIGHT'S THE KING OF BABYLON
CONTEST.

03:41.389 --> 03:43.291
- OH, MICHAEL,
I'M TOO OLD FOR THAT SHIT.

03:43.324 --> 03:44.358
- NO, YOU'RE NOT.

03:44.392 --> 03:45.693
- YES, I AM.

03:45.726 --> 03:47.361
- LOOK, IF THE GUYS SAW

03:47.395 --> 03:48.996
HOW INCREDIBLY SEXY YOU LOOK
IN THOSE JEANS,

03:49.029 --> 03:52.633
THEY'D PROBABLY STOP, UM--

03:52.666 --> 03:54.335
- WHAT?
- NOTHING, NEVER MIND.

03:54.368 --> 03:56.337
I SHOULDN'T HAVE SAID ANYTHING.
- NO, NO, NO.

03:56.370 --> 03:58.872
FINISH WHAT
YOU WERE GOING TO SAY.

03:58.906 --> 04:01.375
- I BET THEY'D STOP MAKING JOKES
ABOUT ADULT DIAPERS

04:01.409 --> 04:03.811
AND DENTURE CREAM AND...

04:03.844 --> 04:05.813
PENILE IMPLANTS.

04:05.846 --> 04:07.681
- PENILE IMPLANTS?

04:07.715 --> 04:09.517
- WELL, HEY,
YOU SAID IT YOURSELF,

04:09.550 --> 04:11.685
YOU'RE TOO OLD FOR THIS SHIT.

04:17.791 --> 04:20.761
[techno music]

04:20.794 --> 04:22.496
*

04:22.530 --> 04:25.499
- I KNEW
THEY WOULDN'T COME.

04:25.533 --> 04:26.667
MICHAEL PROBABLY
HAD TO GIVE THE OLD MAN

04:26.700 --> 04:28.502
A PROSTATE MASSAGE.

04:28.536 --> 04:30.371
- THERE ARE WORSE WAYS
TO SPEND A SATURDAY NIGHT.

04:30.404 --> 04:31.672
- HEY, BOYS.

04:31.705 --> 04:33.441
SORRY WE'RE LATE.

04:33.474 --> 04:35.643
HAD TO WAIT FOR DAVID
TO FINISH HIS 1,000 SIT-UPS.

04:35.676 --> 04:37.578
- YEAH.

04:37.611 --> 04:39.847
- WOW.

04:39.880 --> 04:42.049
DAVID, YOU--
YOU LOOK...GREAT.

04:42.082 --> 04:44.718
I MEAN,
IT'S GREAT TO SEE YOU.

04:44.752 --> 04:45.986
- YEAH!
- WHOO!

04:46.019 --> 04:47.455
WHOO!

04:47.488 --> 04:48.756
- OKAY, ENOUGH OF THIS.

04:48.789 --> 04:51.359
LET'S GO INSIDE WHERE
THEY HAVE SOME MORE JEANS.

04:51.392 --> 04:54.061
- YEAH, WHY DON'T YOU
GO BEFORE US?

04:54.094 --> 04:58.666
*

04:58.699 --> 05:02.336
- * TAKE ME NOW

05:02.370 --> 05:05.406
* TAKE ME NOW

05:05.439 --> 05:08.842
* AH-AH

05:08.876 --> 05:12.480
* AH AH

05:12.513 --> 05:13.914
- HEY, LET'S HAVE A DRINK.

05:13.947 --> 05:15.583
ON ME.

05:15.616 --> 05:18.051
- NO, I THINK I'M GOING TO
GO CHECK OUT THE DANCE FLOOR.

05:18.085 --> 05:19.553
- YEAH, ME TOO.

05:19.587 --> 05:20.954
- SAME HERE.

05:20.988 --> 05:26.093
- THANKS ANYWAY.

05:26.126 --> 05:29.530
- GUESS I WON'T BE WINNING
ANY POPULARITY CONTEST TONIGHT.

05:32.733 --> 05:36.036
- IT'S NOT YOUR PROBLEM.

05:36.069 --> 05:39.907
IT'S THEIRS.
COME ON.

05:39.940 --> 05:40.974
- HEY, DUDE.

05:41.008 --> 05:41.975
- HOW'S IT GOING?

05:42.009 --> 05:43.511
- HAVEN'T SEEN YOU AROUND.

05:43.544 --> 05:46.547
- I'VE BEEN AWAY.

05:46.580 --> 05:47.881
- WELCOME BACK.

05:47.915 --> 05:49.717
NEED A FAVOR?

05:49.750 --> 05:51.552
- NO, THANKS.

05:53.921 --> 05:55.022
- WHO'S THAT?

05:55.055 --> 05:59.460
- NOBODY.

05:59.493 --> 06:01.395
MY DEALER.

06:03.897 --> 06:04.965
EX-DEALER.

06:04.998 --> 06:06.400
- I KNEW WE SHOULDN'T
HAVE COME HERE.

06:06.434 --> 06:08.602
- IT'S OKAY.

06:08.636 --> 06:10.504
I'M OKAY.

06:16.043 --> 06:21.615
LOOK, YOU HAVE TO TRUST ME,
OKAY?

06:21.649 --> 06:23.784
- I DO.

06:29.657 --> 06:30.724
LET'S DANCE.

06:32.826 --> 06:39.933
*

06:39.967 --> 06:42.803
- GENTLEMEN AND GENTLEMEN,

06:42.836 --> 06:45.205
