FOR THE EVENING,

06:45.238 --> 06:48.942
HER ROYAL RUDENESS,
SHEBA,

06:48.976 --> 06:51.044
QUEEN OF BABYLON.

06:51.078 --> 06:54.682
[cheering]

06:54.715 --> 07:02.723
*

07:07.194 --> 07:11.098
- [grunts]

07:11.131 --> 07:13.667
