THE ROYAL TITS ARE INTACT.

07:13.701 --> 07:14.702
[laughter]

07:14.735 --> 07:16.537
ALL RIGHT, BOYS, GO AWAY.

07:16.570 --> 07:18.639
GO PLAY WITH YOURSELVES.
CH-CIAO.

07:18.672 --> 07:19.640
[laughter]

07:19.673 --> 07:20.841
[sighs]

07:20.874 --> 07:25.012
WELCOME TO THE 73rd ANNUAL
ACADEMY A...

07:25.045 --> 07:26.980
OOPS, WRONG SHOW.

07:27.014 --> 07:29.983
WELCOME TO THE KING OF
BABYLON CONTEST...

07:30.017 --> 07:31.585
[cheers and applause]

07:31.619 --> 07:33.554
WHERE THE COMPETITION
IS STIFF

07:33.587 --> 07:35.723
