ALL THE MISPLACED EMPHASIS

40:43.709 --> 40:45.611
ON SMOOTH, MUSCULAR BODIES,

40:45.644 --> 40:47.813
THE OBSESSION WITH YOUTH,
AND THE SHALLOW VALUES.

