DON'T YOU WANT TO--

41:13.939 --> 41:18.243
- I ALREADY TOLD YOU,
I'D RATHER BE WITH YOU.

41:18.276 --> 41:23.048
- I KNOW, BUT...

41:23.081 --> 41:25.016
IS THERE SOME SORT OF...

41:25.050 --> 41:26.985
- WHAT?

41:27.018 --> 41:28.253
- PROBLEM
ON ACCOUNT OF ME?

41:28.286 --> 41:30.522
- OF COURSE NOT.
- BECAUSE IF THERE IS,

41:30.556 --> 41:33.124
I DON'T WANT TO COME
BETWEEN YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS.

41:33.158 --> 41:36.528
- YOU'RE NOT.

41:36.562 --> 41:38.897
AND EVEN IF YOU WERE,
IT WOULDN'T MATTER.

41:42.300 --> 41:44.269
- LOOK.

41:44.302 --> 41:46.137
DON'T SAY THAT.

41:46.171 --> 41:49.207
I DON'T WANT TO DO ANYTHING
TO HURT YOU.

41:49.240 --> 41:50.742
IF I EVER THOUGHT
I WAS GONNA COME

41:50.776 --> 41:53.912
BETWEEN YOU
AND YOUR FRIENDS...

41:53.945 --> 41:56.782
- IF A FRIEND OF MINE
HAS A PROBLEM WITH YOU,

41:56.815 --> 42:00.151
