REALLY MY FRIEND TO BEGIN WITH.

42:21.106 --> 42:25.210
- * A BEAUTIFUL ROOM

42:25.243 --> 42:30.048
* A PERFECT WASTE

42:30.081 --> 42:34.786
* ALL DUST UP
AND BEAUTIFUL *

42:34.820 --> 42:39.725
* FOR A POISONOUS TASTE

42:39.758 --> 42:44.195
* EAT THIS LOVE THAT TAKES

42:44.229 --> 42:49.200
* AND NEVER GIVES

42:49.234 --> 42:53.805
* DRINK THIS HEART
THAT ACHES *

42:53.839 --> 42:57.909
* AND NEVER LIVES

42:57.943 --> 43:02.814
* WHAT A BEAUTIFUL RUIN

43:02.848 --> 43:05.316
* THAT WE COULD BE

43:05.350 --> 43:09.087
- [muttering]

43:09.120 --> 43:11.322
- MICHAEL!

43:11.356 --> 43:13.324
- MA, MELANIE,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

43:13.358 --> 43:15.226
- WHERE'S BRIAN?

43:15.260 --> 43:18.964
- I WAS HOPING
MAYBE YOU COULD HELP.

43:18.997 --> 43:21.299
- WELL, I WOULD, DEBBIE,
BUT I CAN'T REALLY OPEN A BANK

43:21.332 --> 43:23.268
ON A SATURDAY NIGHT.

43:23.301 --> 43:25.003
- MAYBE CREDIT CARDS?

43:25.036 --> 43:28.139
- NO, THE MAXIMUM WITHDRAWAL
AT AN ATM IS $500.

43:28.173 --> 43:30.241
