ANY MORE FUCKING DIFFICULT?

43:35.847 --> 43:36.948
- OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT,

43:36.982 --> 43:38.249
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO CALL
A BAIL BONDSMAN.

43:38.283 --> 43:46.257
