43:52.363 --> 43:55.266
- IF YOU CALL THIS NUMBER,

43:55.300 --> 43:57.002
MENTION THIS GUY'S NAME,

43:57.035 --> 43:58.269
HE'LL PUT UP THE BAIL
FOR YOU.

43:58.303 --> 44:01.006
- WHAT WAS THAT ALL ABOUT?

44:01.039 --> 44:05.410
- I ASKED DINO
FOR A FAVOR.

44:05.443 --> 44:06.845
- THANK YOU.

44:06.878 --> 44:07.979
