44:08.013 --> 44:09.715
THANK YOU, UM...

44:09.748 --> 44:10.816
- BLAKE.

44:10.849 --> 44:14.419
- BLAKE.
AH, THANK YOU, I'M DEBBIE.

44:14.452 --> 44:18.289
OH! OH, OH, THANK YOU!

44:18.323 --> 44:20.425
THAT'S SOME FRIEND
YOU'VE GOT.

44:20.458 --> 44:21.693
- YEAH, I LIKE TO THINK SO.

44:21.727 --> 44:23.261
- OH, THANK YOU!

44:23.294 --> 44:24.896
