TO BE ASHAMED OF, UNCLE VIC.

45:08.306 --> 45:10.776
WE KNOW YOU'RE INNOCENT.

45:10.809 --> 45:12.744
- I JUST WANT TO GO HOME.
CAN WE PLEASE GO HOME?

45:12.778 --> 45:14.379
- YES, I'LL TAKE YOU HOME
RIGHT NOW.

45:14.412 --> 45:16.447
BUT FIRST I WANT YOU
TO TAKE YOUR MEDS.

45:16.481 --> 45:18.449
