YOUR MEDS TO YOU ALL NIGHT.

45:18.483 --> 45:22.754
- IT'S ALL RIGHT, THE DESK
SERGEANT GAVE ME MY PILLS.

45:32.497 --> 45:33.932
- LET'S GO.

45:33.965 --> 45:35.934
- I DON'T THINK
I'VE EVER SEEN YOU SO JEALOUS.

45:35.967 --> 45:37.435
- I AM NOT JEALOUS.

45:37.468 --> 45:38.436
- OH, NOW WHO'S
BEING DISHONEST?

45:38.469 --> 45:40.238
- WELL, HOW WOULD YOU FEEL
IF YOUR BOYFRIEND

45:40.271 --> 45:43.008
WAS BEING OGLED
BY EVERY FAG IN TOWN?

45:43.041 --> 45:45.310
- IT SO HAPPENS, HE IS.

45:45.343 --> 45:46.978
- OH, I AM, YEAH.

45:47.012 --> 45:49.314
- CONSTANTLY.
ONLY YOU NEVER NOTICE.

45:49.347 --> 45:52.250
- YEAH. OH, YEAH. THAT'S
MY PROBLEM, FAULTY GAYDAR.

45:52.283 --> 45:54.119
- LUCKY FOR ME.

45:54.152 --> 45:57.055
- SO NOW THAT YOU'VE PROVEN TO
EVERYONE HOW HOT YOU ARE,

45:57.088 --> 45:58.990
