46:00.892 --> 46:03.328
- NOT EVERY NIGHT.

46:03.361 --> 46:04.963
[chuckles]

46:04.996 --> 46:06.531
BUT IT WAS NICE
TO GET THE ATTENTION,

46:06.564 --> 46:08.366
