I'M STILL ATTRACTIVE.

46:08.399 --> 46:10.902
I MUST ADMIT,
HOT YOUNG MEN

46:10.936 --> 46:15.273
WITH SMOOTH, MUSCULAR BODIES
HAS A CERTAIN APPEAL.

46:15.306 --> 46:17.542
BUT THERE ARE OTHER THINGS.

46:17.575 --> 46:20.846
WORK, MY SON...

46:20.879 --> 46:25.216
AND YOU.

46:25.250 --> 46:27.518
- SAY, BEFORE
YOU HANG THESE JEANS UP

46:27.552 --> 46:29.187
UNTIL NEXT LAUNDRY DAY,

46:29.220 --> 46:31.556
